## Integration with Other Features

### Journal + Daily Analysis

**Workflow:**
1. Run Daily Analysis (4 PM)
2. Review EXIT recommendations
3. **Before exiting:**
   - Open position modal
   - Review entry note
   - Ask: "Did my thesis play out?"
4. Add thoughtful exit note
5. Confirm exit

### Journal + Trade History

**All closed trades automatically include:**
- Entry note (from when you opened position)
- Exit note (from exit modal)
- Tags (carry through from position)

**View in Trade History:**
- Click any row to expand
- See full journal in beautiful layout
- Filter by tags to find specific trades

